{"tid":893414,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"財經台毒瘤——低智仔，不斷散播消極彿系投資思想","createTime":"2018-11-07T15:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T01:47:34.000Z","uid":36454,"like":57,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"14928f5dad08a1ee01d811f2241575a705d13277","tid":893414,"uid":36454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:16:15.000Z","msg":"岩岩入一入低智區<br />\n<br />\n以為去左baby condom<br />\n<br />\n個個自稱早幾年買入/自住驚西<br />\n<br />\n升跌冇所謂，傾下裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喂，阿哥，呢到係財經台，係講投資，資產增值<br />\n<br />\n呢派日日跌<br />\n<br />\n係咪應該傾下睇咩價位放，低位入賺一筆<br />\n<br />\n止賺又好，止蝕又好<br />\n<br />\n絕對唔會係升跌冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n睇得咁開，錢真係冇所謂既，仲投乜撚野資，番鄉下執牛屎啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48af68d32ad5990ecfb0e9d73e75c979ee35f405","tid":893414,"uid":122377,"like":22,"dislike":4,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:45:52.000Z","msg":"Ching 好波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日跌 佢地都會話唔介意<br />\n個時加息 加0.125% 又好開心話好少姐 <br />\n幾百蚊好少錢 個個月比銀行拎到幾舊水都無所謂<br />\n佢地有錢供多D 但無錢裝Now睇英超 要睇俄文台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n業主既生活態度"},{"pid":"94ca0cba3743ac6a90bf4ce6a7d328328c5ebab9","tid":893414,"uid":6297,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"14928f5dad08a1ee01d811f2241575a705d13277","tid":893414,"uid":36454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:16:15.000Z","msg":"岩岩入一入低智區<br />\n<br />\n以為去左baby condom<br />\n<br />\n個個自稱早幾年買入/自住驚西<br />\n<br />\n升跌冇所謂，傾下裝修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n喂，阿哥，呢到係財經台，係講投資，資產增值<br />\n<br />\n呢派日日跌<br />\n<br />\n係咪應該傾下睇咩價位放，低位入賺一筆<br />\n<br />\n止賺又好，止蝕又好<br />\n<br />\n絕對唔會係升跌冇所謂<br />\n<br />\n睇得咁開，錢真係冇所謂既，仲投乜撚野資，番鄉下執牛屎啦 <img src=\"/assets/face