ss=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n業主既生活態度"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"咪係囉, 又話點加息無所謂,食少餐飯,<br />\n跟住早2日HIBOR 1個月回番少少, 唔洗供CAP又勁開心咁討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T16:14:57.000Z","msg":"買平100萬供小4千，買平200萬供小8千<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n慳幾百蚊息就咁開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個市回緊如果真係買左幾年，拿拿臨出貨等細換大啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過睇怕好多都係火棒位貨，綁住走唔甩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真係覺得仲有得gogogo既，仲襯有平貨執，平1x%掃番間，即買即賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過成班同其他人講gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又話自住驚閪，又話市跌加租<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係入多間執平貨就nonono<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n實質就驚到腳都震<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同佢地講事實就話人廢淡買唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n剩係識圍爐扮生活好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾個月自己個低層單位貴樓上高層幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但硬好們都仲夠膽宣傳唔買樓就輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3337950cde68b4caec9901ae23604995fb5dca2","tid":893414,"uid":171446,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd5d2a4d8d7edcc55aaa5da3de4566e4be597c6b","tid":893414,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T16:59:36.000Z","msg":"ho ball"},{"pid":"8e322f9dc224fd39b8938802db4d3e2a508c8543","tid":893414,"uid":171446,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T16:59:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1534ea913fd4c77378a47081fe4d297df8651a1d","tid":893414,"uid":135217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T17:03:19.000Z","msg":"講中晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkg